foods.description: HOLY PEPPERONI, PIZZA SAUCE, MOZZARELLA & PROVOLONE CHEESES WRAPPED IN AN ARTISAN DOUGH STROMBOLI, HOLY PEPPERONI
foods.lowercaseDescription: holy pepperoni, pizza sauce, mozzarella & provolone cheeses wrapped in an artisan dough stromboli, holy pepperoni
foods.ingredients: DOUGH: ENRICHED UNBLEACHED WHEAT FLOUR (WHEAT FLOUR, NIACIN, IRON, THIAMINE MONONITRATE, RIBOFLAVIN, FOLIC ACID), WATER, PALM OIL, SUGAR, SALT, ENRICHED SEMOLINA FLOUR (ENRICHED SEMOLINA, NIACIN, FERROUS SULFATE, THIAMINE MONONITRATE, RIBOFLAVIN, FOLIC ACID), YEAST (YEAST, SORBITAN MONOSTEARATE, ASCORBIC ACID), GARLIC POWDER, DOUGH CONDITIONER (WHEAT FLOUR, ASCORBIC ACID, ENZYMES). FILLING: PEPPERONI BHA, BHT, AND CITRIC ACID ADDED TO HELP PROTECT FLAVOR (PORK, BEEF, SALT, CONTAINS 2% OR LESS: SUGAR, SPICES, OLEORESIN OF PAPRIKA, SODIUM ASCORBATE, NATURAL FLAVORINGS, GARLIC POWDER, DEXTROSE, LACTIC ACID STARTER CULTURE, SODIUM NITRITE, BHA, BHT, CITRIC ACID). CHEESE BLEND (LOW MOISTURE PART-SKIM MOZZARELLA CHEESE [CULTURED PASTEURIZED PART-SKIM MILK, SALT, ENZYMES], PROVOLONE CHEESE [CULTURED PASTEURIZED MILK, SALT, ENZYMES], WATER, FOUR CHEESE FLAVOR (CHEESE BLEND {CHEDDAR CHEESE, PARMESAN CHEESE, ROMANO CHEESE, AND MOZZARELLA CHEESE (PASTEURIZED MILK, CULTURES, SALT, ENZYMES), WHEY PROTEIN CONCENTRATE, MALTODEXTRIN, SALT}]. PIZZA SAUCE (WATER, TOMATO PASTE, SPICE BLEND (SUGAR, SALT, SPICES, LESS THAN 2% SILICON DIOXIDE ADDED TO PREVENT CAKING), GUAR GUM, SOYBEAN OIL, GARLIC PUREE (GARLIC, WATER]). TOPPING: PARMESAN AND ROMANO CHEESE BLEND (PARMESAN CHEESE [MADE FROM COW'S MILK, SALT, ENZYMES], ROMANO CHEESE [MADE FROM COW'S MILK, SALT, ENZYMES], POWDERED CELLULOSE/STARCH BLEND ADDED TO PREVENT CAKING), BREADCRUMBS (BLEACHED FLOUR, WATER, VEGETABLE OIL [SOYBEAN OIL, COTTONSEED OIL, AND/OR CANOLA OIL), SALT, YEAST, CONTAINS 2% OR LESS OF THE FOLLOWING: SUGAR, DEXTROSE), PARSLEY.
